title: You’re Tuned Into the Wrong Station
itunes:title: You’re Tuned Into the Wrong Station
description:
In life, you will get whatever station you are tuned into. The question is, have you been tuning into the wrong station your entire life? In this episode, we’re gonna talk about what station you’re tuned into and I’m gonna teach you how to change that station.
